# 15. Execution flow

## Main generation loop

```python
def run_generation(gen_idx: int):
    population = load_population()
    budget = load_budget()

    parents = select_parents(population, budget)
    children = spawn_children(parents, budget)

    stage1_results = run_stage(children, stage="stage1")
    promoted1 = promote_stage1(stage1_results)

    stage2_results = run_stage(promoted1, stage="stage2")
    promoted2 = promote_stage2(stage2_results)

    stage3_results = run_stage(promoted2, stage="stage3")

    survivors = choose_survivors(
        old_population=population,
        stage3_results=stage3_results,
        diversity_enabled=True
    )

    update_lineages(stage1_results, stage2_results, stage3_results)
    update_memory()
    save_population(survivors)
    write_generation_report(gen_idx)
```

