# 25. Clean v1 success definition

Call v1 successful only if all are true:

* it autonomously runs multiple generations
* it produces a lineage history
* the best evolved pipeline beats the locked baseline on frozen holdout
* the improvement survives at least 2 seeds
* total search cost stays within the fixed budget
* you can explain which mutations led to the win

